'''''The Burial of Kojo''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Gana]] yasohotse 2018 yanditswe, yahimbwe kandi iyobowe na Blitz Bazawule<ref>https://variety.com/2019/film/reviews/the-burial-of-kojo-review-1203212131/</ref> . Yakozwe na Bazawule, Ama K. Abebrese na Kwaku Obeng Boateng,   yafatiwe amashusho yose muri [[Gana]] ku ngengo yimari iciriritse, hamwe nabakozi baho ndetse nabakinnyi benshi ba mbere<ref>http://www.arraynow.com/the-burial-of-kojo</ref>.  Iyi filime ivuga amateka ya Kojo, usigaye apfira mu kirombe cya zahabu cyatawe, mu gihe umukobwa we muto Esi yagendaga mu gihugu cy'umwuka kugira ngo amukize<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/28/movies/the-burial-of-kojo-review.html</ref><ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/555605-the-burial-of-kojo</ref>.

Yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi i New York ku ya 21 Nzeri 2018, mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya Urban World<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/the-burial-of-kojo/</ref><ref>https://whatsnewonnetflix.com/usa/1568569/the-burial-of-kojo-2018</ref>,   aho ryamenyekanye nk'Imvugo Nziza (Sinema y'Isi).  Iyi filime yakiriye ibihembo icyenda mu bihembo bya 15 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards kandi yatsindiye bibiri, harimo Filime Nziza Yambere Yakozwe n'Umuyobozi<ref>https://www.newyorker.com/culture/the-front-row/the-burial-of-kojo-reviewed-a-boldly-lyrical-portrait-of-a-young-ghanaian-girl</ref>.  CYatanzwe na ARRAY kandi yasohotse kuri serivise ya Netflix ku ya 31 Werurwe 2019,   ibaye filime ya mbere yo muri [[Gana]] yerekanwe bwa mbere mu bihugu byatoranijwe ku isi, kuri Netflix<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/the-burial-of-kojo-is-a-stunning-directorial-debut-for-a-musician-turned-filmmaker/2019/04/09/9d0236ba-56e7-11e9-9136-f8e636f1f6df_story.html</ref>.   

